@startuml
title Add New Trail

actor User
boundary TrailPanel
control TrailService
database Database

User -> TrailPanel : chooseAddNewTrail()

User -> TrailPanel : enterTrailName(name)
User -> TrailPanel : enterTrailLength(length)
User -> TrailPanel : enterElevationChanges(elevation)
User -> TrailPanel : uploadTrailPictures(pictures)
User -> TrailPanel : clickSaveTrail()

TrailPanel -> TrailService : addTrail(name, length, elevation, pictures)
TrailService -> Database : insertTrail(name, length, elevation, pictures)
Database --> TrailService : savedTrail
TrailService --> TrailPanel : savedTrail

TrailPanel --> User : displayTrailAddedConfirmation(savedTrail)

@enduml
